inology is, in itself, useful for the elaboration of the final various linguistic versions of the CFR. It finds its place within the materials which will accompany the model rules. Last but by no means least, the revised version of the PECL should be considered by the European institutions as an alternative set of model rules on contract law.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aConflict of lawsxContractszEuropean Union countries. 0aContractszEuropean Union countries. 7aLAW / International.2bisacsh1 aMazeaud, Denis, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist History 2000-2014 (EN)z978311062100608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2009z9783110219517oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2009z978311021952408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET RECHTSWISSENSCHAFTEN 2009z9783899496871oZDB-23-DGC40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978386653725540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783866537255423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783866537255/original  a978-3-11-021952-4  E-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2009b2009  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-062100-6  DGBA Backlist History 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGCb2009  aZDB-23-DGGb2009  aZDB-23-GLAc2000d2014